	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Mar 12th 6:47 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>There are some guides to this around (but of course now I can't remember where).&nbsp;&nbsp;Here is a quick summary:<br><br>(1) You can do it at any level (well I guess you have to be at least 2, so you have more than one song).<br><br>(2) Just play your first song.  As soon as you see its effect message, stop it and play the next song.  When you see its message, switch back to the first song (or you can add a 3rd).<br><br>After your song takes effect, it lasts for a little while.  That allows you to have more than one in effect at once.<br><br>Good luck to you.<br>-- Ekko<br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
